text: Holcoglossum quasipinifolium is a species of plant in the family Orchidaceae. It is found in China and Taiwan. == Sources == * China Plant Specialist Group 2004. Holcoglossum quasipinifolium. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.
